---
title: Double Caribbean-Style Prawns & Carrot Couscous with Charred Corn Salsa & Aioli
description: The couscous is so fluffy that it’s cuddling the fresh prawns in a warm hug. Let those flavours embrace you with Caribbean jerk seasoning and roast veggies with a zap of corn salsa and aioli drizzled over at the end.
